Class ChangeComment

  • java.lang.Object
    • Comment.Comment
      • Comment.ChangeComment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ChangeComment
extends Comment
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class which implements a comment the administrator can make on an offer in order to let the host know what he would need to change if he wants his offer to be approved.
    Author:
    Javier Delgado del Cerro, Javier Lopez Cano
